Taches a completer:

**********************Basic************************
-right div : list of activities
 functionalities:
    -add activity, replaces list
    -

-middle div : edit activity and show stats
functionalities:
    -automatically get activity from user selection
    -display and edit selected activity's fields
    -display a graph or table related to activity

-left div: timer
functionalities:
    -automatically get activity from user selection
    -set the duration
    -run timer with countdown
    -play sound on completion
    -store timed session information when completed

-persistence avec local storage


********************Plus****************************
-new view that opens fullscreen with start of timer
-"winding" timer to set time
-moar stats
-menus that open/close dynamically

